argeted for protection purposes. NFM Group has a reputation of developing products where every detail has a purpose to perform optimally in a system and where every solution can be justified by simplicity, modularity and ability to integrate the user, the tools and the mission. Since formed in 1996, NFM Group have succeeded to become a trustworthy partner within our area of the European defence industry. \r\n','The NFM Group of Companies is comprised of the Norwegian holding company NFM Holding AS, the Norwegian trade division Norsk Forsvarsmateriell, the international marketing division NFM International and the textile production division NFM Production. The most recent subsidary and partner to the NFM Group is NFM Armour and FREC Technology which offers high-tec armour solutions for personal and vehicle protection. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNFM Group is involved in several projects with European governmental bodies and defence forces. In some cases in cooperation with other leading companies in the defence field. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n','','true','2','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-25','true','','true','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 14:26:55','mange','2009-02-25 13:59:10','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:44'),(120,1,1,1,11,54,0,83,0,0,'','','','','','','','','true','2','left','','s_startpic_633709440000000000.jpg','.jpg','true','','','','','0','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 14:28:53','mange','2009-02-23 15:20:49','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:44'),(121,1,1,1,33,55,0,259,0,0,'','','','','The NFM Group Focus Areas','NFM Group develops, manufactures and markets products and services targeted for protection purposes. NFM Group has a reputation of developing products where every detail has a purpose to perform optimally in a system and where every solution can be justified by simplicity, modularity and ability to integrate the user, the tools and the mission. Since formed in 1996, NFM Group have succeeded to become a trustworthy partner within our area of the European defence industry.Tactical textiles by NFM Group enables the user to adapt appearance, protection through the whole spectrum of missions such as delivering humanitarian aid, patrolling the streets, crowd control or fighting a battle. \r\n','The NFM Group of Companies is comprised of the Norwegian holding company NFM Holding AS, the Norwegian trade division Norsk Forsvarsmateriell, the international marketing division NFM International and the textile production division NFM Production. The most recent subsidary and partner to the NFM Group is NFM Armour and FREC Technology which offers high-tec armour solutions for personal and vehicle protection. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNFM Group is involved in several projects with European governmental bodies and defence forces. In some cases in cooperation with other leading companies in the defence field. \r\n','','true','3','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-25','true','','true','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 14:51:32','mange','2009-02-25 13:56:03','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(122,1,1,1,33,56,0,261,0,0,'','','','','','','','','true','3','left','','s_tacticaltextiles_633709440000000000.jpg','.jpg','true','Tactical Textiles','','','','0','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 14:51:39','mange','2009-02-23 14:53:05','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(123,1,1,1,34,57,0,263,0,0,'','','','','Tactical Textiles by the NFM Group','Tactical textiles by NFM Group enables the user to adapt appearance, protection through the whole spectrum of missions such as delivering humanitarian aid, patrolling the streets, crowd control or fighting a battle. \r\n','NFM Group tactical textiles is currently fielded and used in several theatres of battle. From assymetric warfare to conventional battle, NFM Group products are developed to adapt to any mission, threat, climate or environment from jungle to desert, rural and urban. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCurrent productrange includes: &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Load bearing systems and accessories &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Tactical vests and harnesses &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Back packs &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Medic equipment (load bearing) &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Camouflage systems (VIS, NIR, TIR) &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Technical underwear (FR, climate) &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Outer garments &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNFM Group production facilites of tactical textiles are located close to Gdansk &#237;n Poland. Facilities are ISO certified. \r\n','','true','3','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-25','true','','true','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 14:57:11','mange','2009-02-25 13:56:24','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(124,1,1,1,34,58,0,265,0,0,'','','','','','','','','true','3','left','','s_tacticaltextiles_633709440000000000.jpg','.jpg','true','Tactical Textiles','','','','0','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 14:57:14','mange','2009-02-23 14:57:39','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(125,1,1,1,36,59,0,267,0,0,'','','','','','','','','true','3','left','','s_hardbodyarmour_633709440000000000.jpg','.jpg','true','Hard Body Armour','','','','0','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 15:05:30','mange','2009-02-23 15:06:36','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(126,1,1,1,36,60,0,269,0,0,'','','','','Hard Body Armour','NFM Group is a premium manufacturer within the field of hard ballistic armour. The main focus of this dept. is development and production of hard ballistic components and plates for personal use, but the patented technology also offer add-on components for vehicles and installations. \r\n','NFM Group offering consist of: &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- weight and cost optimized solutions &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Patented production technology &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Excellent anti-ballistic properties &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Environmental-friendly materials and production processes &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Recyclable materials &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Flexible shapes and sizes &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Consistent quality through production and product lifespan &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nTo satisfy various requirements we are offering a variety of ceramic core&#180;s as basic components of our hard armour products. These ceramics are then wrapped with a patented process. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nCeramic Core; &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Oxides, Carbides and Glass ceramics. &lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor example: &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Aluminum oxides &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Silicon carbides &lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Boron carbides \r\n','','true','3','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-25','true','','true','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 15:05:32','mange','2009-02-25 13:56:50','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(127,1,1,1,37,61,0,271,0,0,'','','','','','','','','true','3','left','','s_armouring_633709440000000000.jpg','.jpg','true','Armouring &amp; Engineering','','','','0','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 15:09:02','mange','2009-02-23 15:09:37','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(128,1,1,1,37,62,0,273,0,0,'','','','','Armouring &amp; Engineering','NFM Group vehicle armour dept. provides vehicle protection, with a specialization in ballistic armouring. The company provides tailor-made solutions for operations in complex threat environments. Today NFM Group vehicle armour Dept. has more than 20 years experience in delivering protection to an international client base and works with a wide range of materials to produce solutions from lightweight armouring to heavy-duty mine protection. \r\n','With its own proprietary technologies NFM Armour tenders services in all &lt;br /&gt;\r\nconcerned relevant project fields, including: &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Advisory &amp;amp; Consultancy &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Design &amp;amp; Engineering &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Systems Integration &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWith a focus on customer satisfaction and specialization in vehicles operating as: &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Defence vehicles and systems &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Escort &amp;amp; SUV &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Naval vessels &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Installations &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe company&#180;s reputation for a high level of customer satisfaction has attracted &lt;br /&gt;\r\nprestigious clients and a wide range of assignments across Europe. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNFM Armour are able to custom-design solutions according to threat level, &lt;br /&gt;\r\noperational and climatic conditions for vehicle operations. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThrough expert application of the proper ballistic materials, NFM Armour &lt;br /&gt;\r\nprovides ideal solutions that meet operability requirements without &lt;br /&gt;\r\ncompromising safety. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nState-of-the-art composites and ceramic materials have contributed to &lt;br /&gt;\r\nNFM Armour&#180;s reputation in the armouring market. This secure high protection &lt;br /&gt;\r\nis combined with a lower weight penalty, sustainable manoeuvr-ability &lt;br /&gt;\r\nresulting in low fuel consumption and less maintenance compared to traditional &lt;br /&gt;\r\nsystems and this will give reduced life cycle cost. \r\n','','true','3','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-25','true','','true','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 15:09:04','mange','2009-02-25 13:57:11','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(129,1,1,1,38,63,0,275,0,0,'','','','','','','','','true','3','left','','s_flagmap_63370944000000000