es to military and law enforcement organisations. The portfolio consists of both NFM branded products as well as external brands. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe NFM branded products consists of: &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Tactical textiles; &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Personal ballistic protection; &lt;br /&gt;\r\n Armour for vehicles, vessels and installations. &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nExternal brand portfolio includes; &lt;br /&gt;\r\n* Weapons and weapon accessories such as tactical light, laser, sights and electro-optical products &lt;br /&gt;\r\n* Spare parts and equipment for military vehicles, aircraft and airports&#160;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n* EOD products &lt;br /&gt;\r\n* Personal equipment for soldiers and police &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNorsk Forsvarsmateriell is involved in several development projects initiated by the Norwegian Defence Research Establishment (Forsvarets Forskningsinstitutt  FFI) &lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nNorsk Forsvarsmateriell also assists, if or when required, in the formation of industrial offset agreements between Norwegian and foreign defence industries. \r\n','','true','3','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-25','true','','true','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 15:14:05','mange','2009-02-25 13:58:38','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:45'),(133,1,1,1,11,67,0,85,0,0,'','','','','Corporate Profile','To enable the soldier and law enforcement officer with enhanced initiative and capabilities in order to increase survivability, the NFM Group is offering products and services for full spectrum operations developed from understanding and experience of operational requirements.\r\n','','','true','1','left','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23','','','false','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','','2009-02-23 15:20:38','mange','2009-02-23 15:21:39','mange',0,0,'2009-05-18 11:13:44'),(134,1,1,1,11,68,0,87,0,0,'','','','','','',